, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015381, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Let the best of Your Blessings be upon Your noblest creature Muhammad and his Progeny. Please cover them and us and what You favored them and us with under Your Protection, Your Sufficiency, Your Guard, and Your Protecting Cover from all evils and fears in this world and the Hereafter. We are enriched by You and we have sought Your Protection and are honored by You. You are the Undefeatable Winner.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "YAA KHAIRA MAN A-SHAR-TO ILAIY-HE BE-KAFFIJ A’L AFZALA SALA-WAATE-KA A’LAA AF-ZALE KHALQE-KA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE A’LAIY-HE WA A’LAIY-HE-MUS SALAAMO WAJ-A’L-HUM WA IYYAA-NAA WA MAA TA-FAZ-ZALTA BEHI A’LAIY-HIM WA A’LAIY-NAA FEE KANA-FEKA WA HAR-ZEKA WA KEFAA-YATE-KA WA KELAA-ATE-KA WA SITRE-KAL WAAQEE MIN KULLE SOO-IN WA MA-KHOO-FIN FID-DUNYAA WAL AA-KHE-RATE FA-INNAA QADIS TAGH-NAIY-NAA WA’TASAM-NAA WA TA-A’Z-ZAZ-NAA BEKA WA ANTAL GHAALE-BO GHAIY-RO MAGH-LOO-BEEN (AL-MAGH-LOOBE).", "ArabicText1": "يَا خَيْرَ مَنْ اَشَرْتُ اِلَيْهِ بِكَفِّي اجْعَلْ اَفْضَلَ صَلَوَاتِكَ عَلٰى اَفْضَلِ خَلْقِكَ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِهٖ عَلَيْهِ وَعَلَيْهِمُ السَّلَامُ وَاجْعَلْهُمْ وَاِيَّانَا وَمَا تَفَضَّلْتَ بِهٖ عَلَيْهِمْ وَعَلَيْنَا فِيْ كَنَفِكَ وَحِرْزِكَ وَكِفَايَتِكَ وَكِلَاءَتِكَ وَسِتْرِكَ الْوَاقِيْ مِنْ كُلِّ سُوْءٍ وَمَخُوْفٍ فِي الدُّنْيَا وَالْآخِرَةِ فَاِنَّا قَدِ اسْتَغْنَيْنَا وَاعْتَصَمْنَا وَتَعَزَّزْنَا بِكَ وَاَنْتَ الْغَالِبُ غَيْرُ مَغْلُوْبٍ (الْمَغْلُوْبِ)۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "Arab